---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = "About VetList.org | North America's Premier Veterinary Directory";
const description = "Learn about VetList.org's mission to connect pet owners with quality veterinary care across North America. Discover how we're revolutionizing veterinary care discovery.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
        About VetList.org
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Connecting pet owners with exceptional veterinary care across North America through technology, trust, and comprehensive information.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats Banner -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 rounded-xl p-8 mb-12">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 text-center">
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">30,000+</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Listed Practices</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-indigo-600 mb-2">10,000+</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Monthly Visitors</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-600 mb-2">2</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Countries Covered</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">24/7</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Directory Access</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Mission</h2>
        
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          VetList.org was founded with a simple yet powerful mission: to bridge the gap between pet owners seeking quality veterinary care and the dedicated professionals who provide it. In an era where pet ownership has reached unprecedented levels across North America, we recognized the critical need for a comprehensive, reliable, and easily accessible directory that serves both sides of this essential relationship. Our platform has evolved into North America's premier veterinary directory, serving over 10,000 monthly visitors who are actively searching for trusted veterinary services in their communities.
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          What sets VetList.org apart is our commitment to providing detailed, accurate, and up-to-date information about veterinary practices across Canada and the United States. We understand that choosing a veterinarian is one of the most important decisions a pet owner can make, often involving considerations of location, specializations, hours of operation, emergency services, and the specific needs of different types of pets. Our comprehensive database includes over 30,000 veterinary practices, each with detailed profiles that help pet owners make informed decisions about their beloved companions' healthcare needs.
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          For veterinary professionals, VetList.org represents more than just a listing service – it's a powerful marketing and visibility platform that connects them with pet owners in their local communities and beyond. We provide veterinary practices with the tools and exposure they need to grow their client base, showcase their specializations, and communicate their unique value propositions to potential clients. Our platform features advanced search capabilities that allow pet owners to find exactly what they're looking for, whether it's emergency care, exotic pet specialists, equine services, or routine preventive care.
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          The veterinary industry has undergone significant transformation in recent years, with technological advances, changing pet owner expectations, and evolving standards of care creating new opportunities and challenges. VetList.org has positioned itself at the forefront of this evolution, not only by maintaining the most comprehensive directory of veterinary services but also by exploring innovative solutions that can benefit the entire veterinary ecosystem. This includes our development of AI-powered receptionist solutions that help veterinary practices streamline their operations, improve client communication, and enhance the overall experience for both pet owners and veterinary staff.
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Looking toward the future, VetList.org continues to expand its reach and enhance its services, driven by our unwavering commitment to improving the accessibility and quality of veterinary care across North America. We believe that every pet deserves access to excellent veterinary care, and every veterinary professional deserves the opportunity to connect with the pet owners who need their expertise. Through continuous innovation, strategic partnerships, and a deep understanding of both pet owner needs and veterinary practice challenges, VetList.org is building a more connected, efficient, and effective veterinary care ecosystem that benefits everyone involved – most importantly, the millions of beloved pets who depend on quality veterinary care for their health and wellbeing.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- How We Help Section -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">For Pet Owners</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              Find trusted veterinarians in your area quickly and easily
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              Access detailed information about services and specializations
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              View hours of operation and contact information
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              Search by location, services, or specific needs
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              Make informed decisions about your pet's healthcare
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-indigo-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-indigo-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">For Veterinary Practices</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              Increase visibility to thousands of potential clients
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              Showcase specializations and unique services
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              Manage and update practice information easily
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              Connect with pet owners actively seeking care
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              Access to AI-powered practice management solutions
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Technology & Innovation -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Technology & Innovation</h2>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Advanced Search</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Powerful search algorithms help users find exactly what they need based on location, services, and specific requirements.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">AI Solutions</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Cutting-edge AI receptionist technology helps veterinary practices improve efficiency and client communication.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-orange-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-orange-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Real-Time Updates</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Our platform ensures that practice information, hours, and services are always current and accurate.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Contact Section -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-indigo-600 rounded-xl p-8 text-center text-white">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to Get Started?</h2>
        <p class="text-blue-100 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Whether you're a pet owner looking for veterinary care or a veterinary practice wanting to increase your visibility, VetList.org is here to help.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a 
            href="/add-vet" 
            class="bg-white text-blue-600 px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors"
          >
            Add Your Practice
          </a>
          <a 
            href="/contact" 
            class="border-2 border-white text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-white hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors"
          >
            Contact Us
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    /* Custom prose styles */
    .prose h2 {
      color: #1f2937;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .prose p {
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      line-height: 1.75;
    }
    
    /* Custom styles for better visual appeal */
    .shadow-card {
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    }
  </style>
</Layout>